        char = message[i]
        
        # Get index of character in key
        key_index_i = key_index.index(char)
        
        # Determine whether to increment or decrement key_index
        if not inc:
            # Decrement
            key_index_i -= 1
        else:
            # Increment
            key_index_i += 1
        
        # Get character corresponding to key_index
        char_key = key_index[key_index_i % len(key)]
        
        # Add character to message
        message = message[:i] + char_key + message[i+1:]
